<div class="posts">
  {{#each this}}
    <div class="posts__item">
      <div class="posts__item-content">
        <div class="posts__item-top">
          <div class="posts__item-top-main">
            <a href="{{href}}" class="posts__item-avatar-wrap">
              <img src="{{img}}" alt="" class="posts__item-avatar">
            </a>

            <div class="posts__item-top-text">
              <a href="{{href}}" class="posts__item-name">{{name}}</a>
              <p class="posts__item-time">{{time}}</p>
            </div>

          </div>
          <button class="posts__item-top-btn" type="button">
            <svg class="posts__item-pin" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
              <use href="{{assets}}/img/svg-sprite/sprite.svg#pin"></use>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="posts__item-text-wrap info-box">
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Porttitor id eu leo commodo. Lectus egestas risus non semper a. Quis fermentum ultricies sagittis amet et, ac tortor.</p><p><a href='https://www.figma.com/'>Volutpat adipiscing dui proin</a> Volutpat adipiscing dui proin pretium dolor consectetur malesuada faucibus vitae. Sit velit sed enim elementum non nascetur. Volutpat sapien maecenas lectus nulla tincidunt.</p>
        </div>

        {{#if creator}}
        <div class="posts__item-creator">
          <button class="posts__item-creator-photo-wrapper">
            <img src={{creator.photo}} alt="" class="posts__item-creator-photo">
          </button>
          <a href={{creator.href}} class="posts__item-creator-name">
              {{creator.name}}
          </a>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

      </div>

      <div class="posts__item-video-wrapper">
        <a class="posts__item-video" data-fancybox data-fancybox-type="iframe" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJWksPWDKOc&t=7822s">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/1000/1000"
               alt="" 
               class="posts__item-video-img
               {{#if private}} posts__item-video-img_private {{/if }}"
          >

          <div class="posts__item-play-btn">
            <svg class="posts__item-play-btn-icon" viewBox="0 0 20 23">
              <use href="{{assets}}/img/svg-sprite/sprite.svg#triangle"></use>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </a>
        {{#if private}}
        <div class="posts__item-overlay"> 
          <div class="posts__item-unlock">
            <div class="posts__item-unlock-top">
              <svg class="posts__item-unlock--icon" viewBox="0 0 16 21">
                <use href="{{assets}}/img/svg-sprite/sprite.svg#locket"></use>
              </svg>
              <p class="posts__item-unlock--text">Unlock post for</p>
              <span class="posts__item-unlock--price">${{price}}</span>
            </div>
            <button class="posts__item-unlock--button">Unlock now</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>

        <div class="posts__item-footer">
            <div class="posts__item-footer-statistic">

              <div class="posts__item-footer-section">
                <svg class="posts__item-footer-section--icon" width="20" height="19" viewBox="0 0 20 19">
                  <use href="{{assets}}/img/svg-sprite/sprite.svg#like"></use>
                </svg>
              {{likes}}
              </div>
              
              <div class="posts__item-footer-section">
                <svg class="posts__item-footer-section--icon" width="19" height="20" viewBox="0 0 19 20">
                  <use href="{{assets}}/img/svg-sprite/sprite.svg#comments"></use>
                </svg>
              {{comments}}
              </div>
              
            </div>
            <div class="posts__item-footer-section">
              <svg class="posts__item-footer-section--icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 20 23">
                <use href="{{assets}}/img/svg-sprite/sprite.svg#tips"></use>
              </svg>
              <span>Send tip</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  {{/each}}
</div>
